name: Zollerdisplayanalyzer
tagline: Application to test a zoller display analysis class
body:
Application to test a zoller display analysis class

The app is divided in two parts, the gui part and the analysis part.

The analysis part is made to be used in one of my projects on a raspberry pi placed in front of the display of a Zoller tool presetter.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
